text: Shanhe () may refer to these places in China: *Shanhe Subdistrict, a subdistrict of Shuangyang District, Changchun, Jilin *Shanhe Township, a township of Longde County, Ningxia ==Towns== *Shanhe, Gansu, in Zhengning County, Gansu *Shanhe, Heilongjiang, in Wuchang, Heilongjiang *Shanhe, Shanxi, in Zezhou County, Shanxi ==See also== *Sanhe (disambiguation)
title: Shanhe
